[
  {
    "speaker": "char_xiao_ting",
    "speaker_name": "小婷",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "这是我特地要隔壁那洗衣裳的老太婆炖的鸡汤，是乌骨鸡，听说吃了最补，看样子果然有点效。",
    "tone": "温柔",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_xiao_ting",
    "speaker_name": "小婷",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "你说奇不奇怪？我这一辈子从来都没有照顾过别人，也从来没有人照顾过我。",
    "tone": "平静",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_xiao_ting",
    "speaker_name": "小婷",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "我现在才知道，不管被人照顾或照顾别人，原来都是这么……这么好的事。",
    "tone": "欣慰",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_xiao_ting",
    "text": "你叫什么名字？你自己真正的名字。",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_xiao_ting",
    "speaker_name": "小婷",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "我姓周，叫周婷，以前别人都叫我小婷。",
    "tone": "平静",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_xiao_ting",
    "speaker_name": "小婷",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "我没有打扮的时侯，看起来是不是像个老太婆？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_xiao_ting",
    "text": "你不像。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_xiao_ting",
    "speaker_name": "小婷",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "你真是个很奇怪的人，我想不到你还会来找我的。",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_xiao_ting",
    "speaker_name": "小婷",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "你来的时候样子好可怕。我本来以为你已经快死了，我随便问你什么话，你都不知道，可是我一碰你的刀，你就要打人。",
    "tone": "担心",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_xiao_ting",
    "speaker_name": "小婷",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "我知道你是个好人，虽然也轻轻打了我一下，却没有像别人那么污辱我，你还平白无故给了我那么多银子。",
    "tone": "温柔",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_xiao_ting",
    "speaker_name": "小婷",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "你给我的那些银子，我一点也没有用，就算天天买鸡吃，也够用好久了，所以你一定要留在这里，等你的病好了再走。",
    "tone": "恳求",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_xiao_ting",
    "speaker_name": "小婷",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "假如你现在就走了，我一定会很难受很难受的。",
    "tone": "恳求",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_xiao_ting",
    "text": "你这里有没有酒？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_xiao_ting",
    "speaker_name": "小婷",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "这里没有，但是我可以去买。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_xiao_ting",
    "text": "好，你去买，我不走。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_xiao_ting",
    "speaker_name": "小婷",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我虽然什么都不懂，可是我知道你一定很痛苦。",
    "tone": "温柔",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_qi_gai",
    "speaker_name": "乞丐",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "这小屋里住的本来是个婊子，前天晚上却逃走了，所以捕快老爷来抓她。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_qi_gai",
    "text": "为什么要抓她？她为什么要逃？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_qi_gai",
    "speaker_name": "乞丐",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "因为她杀了人。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_qi_gai",
    "text": "她杀了谁？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_qi_gai",
    "speaker_name": "乞丐",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "杀了街头那小酒铺的老板。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_qi_gai",
    "text": "为什么要杀他？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_qi_gai",
    "speaker_name": "乞丐",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "她常去那酒铺买酒，本来是给钱的，可是她酒喝得太多，连生意都不做了，酒瘾发作时，就只好去赊，那肥猪居然就赊给了她。因为那肥猪居然不知道她是干什么的，想打她的主意。前天晚上也不知道为了什么，她居然一个人跑到酒铺里去喝酒，喝得大醉，那肥猪当然心喜倒翻，认为这是天大的好机会，乘她喝醉时，就霸王硬上弓。谁知她虽然是卖笑的，却偏偏不肯让那肥猪碰她，竟拿起了柜上那把切猪肉的刀，一刀将那肥猪的脑袋砍成了两半。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_qi_gai",
    "speaker_name": "乞丐",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "这年头的怪事真不少，婊子居然会为了不肯脱裤子而杀人，你说滑稽不滑稽？",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "我知道……我知道。",
    "tone": "痛苦",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "speaker_name": "多情子",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "干了。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "speaker_name": "多情子",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "好酒量。",
    "tone": "微笑",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "text": "嗯，好酒量。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "speaker_name": "多情子",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "酒量好，刀法也好。",
    "tone": "微笑",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "text": "好刀法。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "speaker_name": "多情子",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "你好像曾经说过，能杀人的刀法，就是好刀法。",
    "tone": "微笑",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "text": "我说过？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "speaker_name": "多情子",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "你知不知道你刚才杀的那个人是谁？",
    "tone": "微笑",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "text": "刚才我杀过人？我杀了谁？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "speaker_name": "多情子",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "你杀的是你大舅子。",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "speaker_name": "多情子",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "你难道忘了现在你已是成过亲的人？你老婆的哥哥，就是你大舅子。",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "speaker_name": "多情子",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "她就是你的小姨子。小姨子就是你老婆的妹妹，也就是你大舅子的妹妹。",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "speaker_name": "多情子",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "你知不知道她现在想干什么？",
    "tone": "微笑",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "speaker_name": "多情子",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "她想杀了你。",
    "tone": "微笑",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "为什么每个人都想杀了我？",
    "tone": "无奈",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "speaker_name": "多情子",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "你说得一点都不错，这屋里坐着十三个人，至少有七个是来杀你的，他们都想等你喝醉了再动手。",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "text": "要等我喝醉？我怎么会醉？再喝三天三夜都不会醉。",
    "tone": "平静",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "speaker_name": "多情子",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "既然再等三天三夜都没有用，看来他们现在就会动手了。",
    "tone": "微笑",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_hei_shou_fu_chou",
    "speaker_name": "黑手复仇年轻人",
    "listener": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "text": "黑手复仇，道上的朋友莫管闲事。",
    "tone": "厉声",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_hei_shou_fu_chou",
    "speaker_name": "黑手复仇年轻人",
    "listener": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "text": "你是什么人？",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "speaker_name": "多情子",
    "listener": "char_hei_shou_fu_chou",
    "text": "我的姓名一向不告诉死人的。",
    "tone": "淡然",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_hei_shou_fu_chou",
    "speaker_name": "黑手复仇年轻人",
    "listener": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "text": "谁是死人？",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "speaker_name": "多情子",
    "listener": "char_hei_shou_fu_chou",
    "text": "你！",
    "tone": "冷酷",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "text": "称赞你什么？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "speaker_name": "多情子",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "难道你看不出我用的是什么功夫？",
    "tone": "微笑",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "text": "我看不出。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "speaker_name": "多情子",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "这就是'天地交征阴阳大悲赋'中，惟一流传到人世的两种功夫之一。",
    "tone": "得意",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "text": "哦？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "speaker_name": "多情子",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "这就是天绝地灭大搜魂手。",
    "tone": "得意",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "text": "哦？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "speaker_name": "多情子",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "还有一种，就是你已学会的天移地转大移穴法。你能将穴道移开一寸，至少已将这种功夫练到了九成火候。",
    "tone": "得意",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "text": "你呢？你是谁？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "speaker_name": "多情子",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "我就是西方星宿海的多情子，甚至比你还多情。",
    "tone": "微笑",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "text": "多情人也杀人？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "speaker_name": "多情子",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "情到浓时情转薄。就因为我的情太多太浓，所以现在比纸还薄。只不过我也从来不会无缘无故就杀人的。",
    "tone": "淡然",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "speaker_name": "多情子",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "我杀这些人，只因为我不想让你死在他们手里。",
    "tone": "认真",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "text": "为什么？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "speaker_name": "多情子",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "因为我想要你死在我手里。",
    "tone": "认真",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "text": "你真的想？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "speaker_name": "多情子",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "我简直想得要命。",
    "tone": "认真",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ni_hui",
    "speaker_name": "倪慧",
    "listener": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "text": "因为他若杀了你，我就嫁给他。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "speaker_name": "多情子",
    "listener": "char_ni_hui",
    "text": "你看，我已经三十五了，还没有娶妻，当然也没有儿子。不孝有三，无后为大，你总不能叫我做个不孝的人。",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ni_hui",
    "speaker_name": "倪慧",
    "listener": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "text": "他不会的。",
    "tone": "肯定",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "speaker_name": "多情子",
    "listener": "char_ni_hui",
    "text": "你怎么知道？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ni_hui",
    "speaker_name": "倪慧",
    "listener": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "text": "我看见过他三次出手，他的刀上本来的确就好像有鬼一样。",
    "tone": "认真",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "speaker_name": "多情子",
    "listener": "char_ni_hui",
    "text": "现在呢？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ni_hui",
    "speaker_name": "倪慧",
    "listener": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "text": "现在他刀上的鬼已经到他自己心里去了。",
    "tone": "肯定",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "speaker_name": "多情子",
    "listener": "char_ni_hui",
    "text": "怎么会去的？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ni_hui",
    "speaker_name": "倪慧",
    "listener": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "text": "为了两样事。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "speaker_name": "多情子",
    "listener": "char_ni_hui",
    "text": "酒和女人？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ni_hui",
    "speaker_name": "倪慧",
    "listener": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "text": "为了这两样事，以前他也几乎死过一次。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "speaker_name": "多情子",
    "listener": "char_ni_hui",
    "text": "可是他没有死。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ni_hui",
    "speaker_name": "倪慧",
    "listener": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "text": "因为他有个好朋友！",
    "tone": "肯定",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "speaker_name": "多情子",
    "listener": "char_ni_hui",
    "text": "叶开？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ni_hui",
    "speaker_name": "倪慧",
    "listener": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "text": "只可惜现在叶开已不知到哪里去了。",
    "tone": "无奈",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "speaker_name": "多情子",
    "listener": "char_ni_hui",
    "text": "那么现在他岂非很危险？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ni_hui",
    "speaker_name": "倪慧",
    "listener": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "text": "危险得很。",
    "tone": "肯定",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "speaker_name": "多情子",
    "listener": "char_ni_hui",
    "text": "你看我是不是接得住他的刀？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ni_hui",
    "speaker_name": "倪慧",
    "listener": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "text": "你那大搜魂手连真的鬼魂都能抓住，何况一把已没有鬼的刀？",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "speaker_name": "多情子",
    "listener": "char_ni_hui",
    "text": "就算我能抓住他的刀，我的手岂非也会断？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ni_hui",
    "speaker_name": "倪慧",
    "listener": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "text": "不会的。",
    "tone": "肯定",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "speaker_name": "多情子",
    "listener": "char_ni_hui",
    "text": "为什么不会？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ni_hui",
    "speaker_name": "倪慧",
    "listener": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "text": "因为你抓的法子很巧妙，你的手根本碰不到刀锋，而且你另一只手已搜去了他的魂。",
    "tone": "认真",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "speaker_name": "多情子",
    "listener": "char_ni_hui",
    "text": "这么说来，他这个人岂非已完了？",
    "tone": "得意",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ni_hui",
    "speaker_name": "倪慧",
    "listener": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "text": "他还有一点希望。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "speaker_name": "多情子",
    "listener": "char_ni_hui",
    "text": "什么希望？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ni_hui",
    "speaker_name": "倪慧",
    "listener": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "text": "只要他告诉我们两件事，我们连碰都不碰他。",
    "tone": "认真",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "speaker_name": "多情子",
    "listener": "char_ni_hui",
    "text": "两件什么事？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ni_hui",
    "speaker_name": "倪慧",
    "listener": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "text": "孔雀翎在哪里？天地交征阴阳大悲赋在哪里？",
    "tone": "认真",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "speaker_name": "多情子",
    "listener": "char_ni_hui",
    "text": "他若有孔雀翎，若已练成了大悲赋，我们就完了。",
    "tone": "认真",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ni_hui",
    "speaker_name": "倪慧",
    "listener": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "text": "也许他的手已不够稳，已没法子使用孔雀翎；也许他虽然练成了大移穴法，却已没法子再练别的功夫了。",
    "tone": "认真",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "speaker_name": "多情子",
    "listener": "char_ni_hui",
    "text": "看他这样子，的确好像没法子再练别的功夫了。",
    "tone": "微笑",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ni_hui",
    "speaker_name": "倪慧",
    "listener": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "text": "现在他惟一还能练的功夫，就是喝酒。",
    "tone": "嘲讽",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "speaker_name": "多情子",
    "listener": "char_ni_hui",
    "text": "这种功夫他好像已练得很不错。",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ni_hui",
    "speaker_name": "倪慧",
    "listener": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "text": "只可惜这种功夫惟一的用处就是让他变成个酒鬼，死酒鬼。",
    "tone": "嘲讽",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "speaker_name": "多情子",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "看样子他像已决心不肯说？",
    "tone": "无奈",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ni_hui",
    "speaker_name": "倪慧",
    "listener": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "text": "也许他一定要等到快死的时候才肯说。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "speaker_name": "多情子",
    "listener": "char_ni_hui",
    "text": "现在时候还没有到？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ni_hui",
    "speaker_name": "倪慧",
    "listener": "char_duo_qing_zi",
    "text": "你一出手就到了。",
    "tone": "肯定",
    "chapter": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ni_hui",
    "speaker_name": "倪慧",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "难道你不认得我了？我就是倪家的二小姐，倪慧，我们是朋友。",
    "tone": "恐惧",
    "chapter": 18
  }
]